ccmath-cpp (2.2.1-2) unstable; urgency=medium

    * Added subset of original ccmath files to support eigenvalues and eigenvectors computation.
    * Subset of original ccmath files from http://freecode.com/projects/ccmath version 2.2.1; .c files (all from ccmath/matrix/) renamed to .cc
    * C++-ified by lab
    * Update package version to 2.2.1-2, using so.1.1.0 since it is a backwards compatible change. Also improve some code comments.

 -- Roel van de Kraats <roel@2getthere.eu>  Thu, 11 Apr 2019 14:00:20 +0200

ccmath-cpp (2.2.1-1) unstable; urgency=medium

    * Subset of original ccmath files from http://freecode.com/projects/ccmath version 2.2.1; .c files (all from ccmath/matrix/) renamed to .cc
    * C++-ify source files. Add header for the selected set of functions, using documentation from ccmath-2.2.1/manual/C01-matrix.
    * Add cmake scripts for building and creating deb and/or rpm packages.

